"""Cavern debris prop sprites (b495).

Small pixel-art props stamped onto plain cavern floors by the
procedural renderer (cavern_render.py), replacing the b494
vector-drawn debris kit. Sliced from two hand-painted debris sheets,
checker-keyed to alpha, cropped, capped at 40px, WebP q80.

Deliberately excluded: anything that reads as LOOT or interactables
(bottles/potions, gold, scrolls, weapons, armor, candles/torches) so
decorations never bait a tap.
"""

